comments: Conley (UTA) is already in Morris' (DEN) path and does not deliver contact as the defenders switch.
Forbes (DEN) moves laterally into Forrest's (UTA) body as he is gathering the ball and affects his driving shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (UTA) and Reed (DEN) make incidental foot to foot contact with one another as they disengage on the perimeter.
Bogdanovic (UTA) is moving alongside Morris' (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Nnaji (DEN) and Gay (UTA) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Conley (UTA) makes clean contact with the ball and strips it from Barton's (DEN) control.  A jump ball is not warranted because Conley is able to gain sole possession of the ball.
O'Neale (UTA) is already in Morris' (DEN) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Morris (DEN) places his hand momentarily on O'Neale's (UTA) hip and marginal contact occurs as Morris slides his hand off of O'Neale.
Barton (DEN) makes clean contact with the ball as simultaneous incidental body contact occurs with O'Neale (UTA).
Bogdanovic (UTA) is moving alongside Morris' (DEN) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive.
Morris (DEN) and O'Neale (UTA) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Morris (DEN) brings his hand forward towards Conley (UTA) and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Morris (DEN) applies a stayed hand to Conley's (UTA) hip and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
O'Neale (UTA) steps slightly forward towards Barton's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.

Replay review of the foul called on Gay (UTA) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Gay does not maintain verticality and makes contact with Barton's (DEN) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Barton (DEN) commits a take foul on Gay (UTA).
Forrest (UTA) and Forbes (DEN) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs as Forbes secures the ball.
Forrest (UTA) brushes Forbes' (DEN) arm after initially making contact with the ball, and the arm contact is marginal.
Reed (DEN) is moving alongside Conley's (UTA) path with his arm slightly extended forward and marginal contact occurs in the backcourt.
Reed (DEN) commits a take foul on Bogdanovic (UTA).
Conley (UTA) steps slightly towards Forbes (DEN) and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
